1
00:00:00,140 --> 00:00:02,700
Welcome to the finals of our Kids Plus contest

2
00:00:02,780 --> 00:00:06,640
Today, one lucky person will be chosen as the new Kids Plus spokesperson

3
00:00:09,480 --> 00:00:13,660
Mireille! Mireille! Mireille!

4
00:00:13,700 --> 00:00:14,300
Hello

5
00:00:14,340 --> 00:00:14,820
Mireille, Mireille, Aurore

6
00:00:14,860 --> 00:00:17,680
Take it easy, take it easy! We started with 5,000 match races, and with our viewers' help, we've narrowed down the contestants

7
00:00:17,740 --> 00:00:21,459
to these two incredible young women

8
00:00:21,460 --> 00:00:22,779
Yes

9
00:00:22,780 --> 00:00:25,459
And now let's invite our wonderful finalists

10
00:00:25,460 --> 00:00:29,719
On my right, Aurore Beauréal, and on my left, Mireille Caquet

11
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:32,779
Who will be the lucky winner? Find out now

12
00:00:32,780 --> 00:00:33,540
One for Aurore,

13
00:00:33,580 --> 00:00:38,639
two for Mireille. Make your choice, and don't forget, messages are charged

14
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:41,479
Come on, Manon, give it back

15
00:00:41,480 --> 00:00:45,779
But I want to be a fashion designer too

16
00:00:45,780 --> 00:00:48,160
Manon, please, it's not finished yet, you'll ruin it

17
00:00:59,860 --> 00:01:00,820
Hmph

18
00:01:03,280 --> 00:01:04,499
Ah, ah

19
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:06,239
I'll vote for Mireille

20
00:01:06,240 --> 00:01:07,179
She's the best

21
00:01:07,180 --> 00:01:10,699
Hey, that's my phone!

22
00:01:10,700 --> 00:01:12,119
Ah

23
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:14,779
Why did I agree to do this?

24
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:16,179
It's not like she even noticed

25
00:01:16,180 --> 00:01:19,020
Don't worry, if you can handle Manon one day,

26
00:01:19,100 --> 00:01:25,959
all the future villains will seem easy

27
00:01:25,960 --> 00:01:28,200
Alya, I've got a big job for you

28
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:32,779
Guess who's shooting in the park?

29
00:01:32,780 --> 00:01:34,119
Ah, right now?

30
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:35,939
Adrien, in the park,

31
00:01:35,940 --> 00:01:38,019
right now, as we speak

32
00:01:38,020 --> 00:01:38,839
Oh my gosh

33
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:41,179
So what do I say to him?

34
00:01:41,180 --> 00:01:42,719
The usual stuff

35
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:45,939
I, uh...

36
00:01:45,940 --> 00:01:48,239
Stop that

37
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:49,979
And who's this?

38
00:01:49,980 --> 00:01:52,639
No way, I forgot about that little detail

39
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:54,379
And who is this?

40
00:01:54,380 --> 00:01:56,580
That's Manon, the daughter of one of my mom's friends

41
00:01:56,660 --> 00:01:58,419
I'm watching her this afternoon

42
00:01:58,420 --> 00:02:00,039
No, I can't go out

43
00:02:00,040 --> 00:02:01,040
Wait, let me guess

44
00:02:01,100 --> 00:02:03,120
one more favor you couldn't say no to

45
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:05,139
No, I just...

46
00:02:05,140 --> 00:02:07,499
couldn't say no

47
00:02:07,500 --> 00:02:12,959
Look, it's okay, I can handle your little detail

48
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:15,539
Oh thanks, but I'm responsible for her

49
00:02:15,540 --> 00:02:18,719
Besides, I couldn't ask you to... ooh

50
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:21,780
She's a total angel

51
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:25,699
Manon, put it down

52
00:02:25,700 --> 00:02:32,779
Come back!

53
00:02:32,780 --> 00:02:34,399
You're such a pushover, Marinette

54
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:36,919
I've babysat my siblings many times

55
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:40,279
That makes me an expert at dealing with angels

56
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:42,499
Who do you think you are, tell me?

57
00:02:42,500 --> 00:02:46,319
I'm a legendary unicorn, transformed into a fabulous human girl in the Miraculous world

58
00:02:46,320 --> 00:02:48,219
a legendary unicorn

59
00:02:48,220 --> 00:02:54,139
I grant wishes, but only the wishes of well-behaved little ones

60
00:02:54,140 --> 00:02:56,439
No, you don't

61
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:56,900
Or else?

62
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:04,479
Okay, we're all going to the park

63
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:06,119
Yay!

64
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:09,879
Alright

65
00:03:09,880 --> 00:03:12,019
This is the moment we've been waiting for

66
00:03:12,020 --> 00:03:14,159
Our home viewers have made their decision

67
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:17,719
And the new Kids Plus weather girl

68
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:21,679
is Mireille!

69
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,379
She totally beat you, Aurore

70
00:03:23,380 --> 00:03:25,619
Next time

71
00:03:25,620 --> 00:03:26,419
What's wrong?

72
00:03:26,420 --> 00:03:29,519
You just lost half a million votes, that's all

73
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:31,799
The vibrations are so strong

74
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:34,759
I can feel sudden anger and sadness

75
00:03:34,760 --> 00:03:37,819
My next victim's moment of weakness

76
00:03:37,820 --> 00:03:41,480
will be an easy target for my akumas

77
00:04:00,920 --> 00:04:02,539
I should have won

78
00:04:02,540 --> 00:04:05,579
Talent, star beauty, I've got everything

79
00:04:05,580 --> 00:04:07,479
But she took everything from me

80
00:04:07,480 --> 00:04:09,219
They took everything from me

81
00:04:09,220 --> 00:04:11,540
They... *sob*

82
00:04:21,300 --> 00:04:22,859
You're absolutely right

83
00:04:22,860 --> 00:04:25,819
You should have won, yes

84
00:04:25,820 --> 00:04:28,159
I should have won

85
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:30,919
Stormy Weather, I am Hawk Moth

86
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:35,299
I'm giving you the power to fight them as my weather girl

87
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:38,339
All you have to do is bring me the Miraculous

88
00:04:38,340 --> 00:04:40,099
Can you do that?

89
00:04:40,100 --> 00:04:41,459
Yes

90
00:04:41,460 --> 00:04:43,679
That's my weather girl

91
00:04:43,680 --> 00:04:48,480
Show the whole world who the best weather girl is

92
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:58,659
Okay, we're going to go over there very calmly

93
00:04:58,660 --> 00:05:01,279
as if we're just passing by

94
00:05:01,280 --> 00:05:03,760
Then, then we'll watch the shoot

95
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:06,299
Finally, I'll invite her for juice

96
00:05:06,300 --> 00:05:09,639
Then we'll get married, live happily in a nice house

97
00:05:09,640 --> 00:05:12,340
Two... no, no, three kids and a dog

98
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:13,239
maybe a cat

99
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:15,980
Oh, forget the cat, I'm allergic anyway

100
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:18,439
Let's start by walking past her

101
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:22,119
Let's see if we can get that juice

102
00:05:22,120 --> 00:05:22,739
Awesome

103
00:05:22,740 --> 00:05:23,379
Super

104
00:05:23,380 --> 00:05:25,140
I want to see hunger in your eyes

105
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:32,519
Remember, stay calm, stay calm

106
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:34,479
We couldn't be more obvious

107
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:38,000
Okay, let's start over

108
00:05:43,580 --> 00:05:45,979
She waved at me when she saw this

109
00:05:45,980 --> 00:05:47,419
Yeah, I saw it too

110
00:05:47,420 --> 00:05:50,620
That's totally normal, we're in the same class

111
00:05:57,640 --> 00:06:01,179
Hmm

112
00:06:01,180 --> 00:06:02,859
I am Stormy Weather

113
00:06:02,860 --> 00:06:06,839
the only weather girl who predicts the weather correctly

114
00:06:06,840 --> 00:06:11,859
And lucky for you, a cold front is coming your way

115
00:06:11,860 --> 00:06:14,879
Now

116
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:17,000
Get me out of here! Help!

117
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:19,119
Help!

118
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,719
Bravo, that's it!

119
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:23,319
Your mom brought the spaghetti, give me that smile

120
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:26,599
Okay, now no, your mom dropped the spaghetti

121
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:29,359
And now you have to eat it off the floor

122
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:34,879
Yes, you're so angry, show me that anger

123
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:37,320
Marinette, I want a balloon that says "Mireille" on it

124
00:06:37,380 --> 00:06:39,059
Can I have one?

125
00:06:39,060 --> 00:06:39,939
Marinette?

126
00:06:39,940 --> 00:06:42,319
Marinette!

127
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:44,239
Silence!

128
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:46,740
Come here, little one, I'll get you that balloon

129
00:06:46,780 --> 00:06:50,919
No, I want to go with Marinette

130
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,239
I'll handle it

131
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:53,380
I'm her babysitter

132
00:06:55,700 --> 00:06:57,039
What about Adrien?

133
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:59,159
Mireille?

134
00:06:59,160 --> 00:06:59,880
Mireille?

135
00:07:02,640 --> 00:07:05,219
Mireille? Where is Mireille?

136
00:07:05,220 --> 00:07:09,979
I advise those who voted for Mireille to go inside

137
00:07:09,980 --> 00:07:12,659
Because it's about to get very stormy

138
00:07:12,660 --> 00:07:13,839
Wait a minute

139
00:07:13,840 --> 00:07:16,340
Too late

140
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,840
Let's go back

141
00:07:27,880 --> 00:07:29,999
I want to ride the ant

142
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,559
No, no, not now

143
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:34,619
I have to get back to Adrien

144
00:07:34,620 --> 00:07:36,319
You promised

145
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:39,359
You're not going to break your promise, are you?

146
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:41,899
Oh, please! No puppy dog eyes

147
00:07:41,900 --> 00:07:45,899
You know I can't say no to them, don't you?

148
00:07:45,900 --> 00:07:46,140
Ah!

149
00:08:04,580 --> 00:08:07,859
No, no, no, the kid ate too much spaghetti

150
00:08:07,860 --> 00:08:11,459
We need more energy, more romance

151
00:08:11,460 --> 00:08:14,619
What we need is a girl

152
00:08:14,620 --> 00:08:15,580
I need a model

153
00:08:15,620 --> 00:08:16,859
Who, me?

154
00:08:16,860 --> 00:08:21,019
Yes, to pose with Mr. Adrien

155
00:08:21,020 --> 00:08:23,539
I don't think you want me

156
00:08:23,540 --> 00:08:26,159
I'm having an allergic reaction to this apple

157
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,440
Miss Azami Kiki Marble

158
00:08:27,520 --> 00:08:31,619
don't go anywhere, okay?

159
00:08:31,620 --> 00:08:33,779
They need a model to pose with Adrien

160
00:08:33,780 --> 00:08:35,260
What? Are you serious?

161
00:08:35,300 --> 00:08:36,780
Is that boy your boyfriend?

162
00:08:36,860 --> 00:08:41,039
What? No, I mean yes, no...

163
00:08:41,040 --> 00:08:43,019
Just admit it, what are you waiting for?

164
00:08:43,020 --> 00:08:45,960
What about Manon?

165
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:50,060
You handle the handsome prince

166
00:08:50,140 --> 00:08:52,459
I'll handle the lady unicorn here

167
00:08:52,460 --> 00:08:54,459
You don't know how to control her anyway

168
00:08:54,460 --> 00:08:55,060
Impossible

169
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:57,039
My flow is Marinette, for once

170
00:08:57,040 --> 00:08:58,539
Trust me

171
00:08:58,540 --> 00:09:00,339
Yeehaw, unicorns unite

172
00:09:00,340 --> 00:09:04,598
Let's go find ourselves some sad peasant kids and grant their wishes

173
00:09:04,599 --> 00:09:06,099
Yeehaa!

174
00:09:06,100 --> 00:09:09,280
Yeehaaa!

175
00:09:27,940 --> 00:09:28,720
Time to transform

176
00:09:28,780 --> 00:09:28,980
Tikki?

177
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:35,640
Spots on! Yes!

178
00:09:48,740 --> 00:09:49,380
No

179
00:09:56,760 --> 00:09:58,179
Plagg? Plagg!

180
00:09:58,180 --> 00:09:59,559
I'm not here

181
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:02,560
I'm sleeping

182
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:09,720
For your information, I can smell Camembert even in my sleep

183
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:11,999
That's one of my many talents

184
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:14,359
Great, but there's no time to talk about cheese

185
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:17,640
Plagg, claws out!

186
00:10:34,980 --> 00:10:38,079
Why did I leave her with him? I shouldn't have done this

187
00:10:38,080 --> 00:10:41,819
No, Alya's right, she's in good hands, I have to trust her

188
00:10:41,820 --> 00:10:46,219
I'll get you out of there

189
00:10:46,220 --> 00:10:47,940
Oh, let's cut that iced cake

190
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:51,399
Huh? Ah!

191
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:52,499
Huh!

192
00:10:52,500 --> 00:10:54,480
Or let's not cut it, we're going to Plan B

193
00:10:54,540 --> 00:10:57,779
Huh! Don't worry, everything will be fine

194
00:10:57,780 --> 00:10:59,279
Where's Marinette?

195
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:01,199
She hasn't forgotten you, Manon

196
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:04,259
How do you know Adrien?

197
00:11:04,260 --> 00:11:05,479
Marinette told me

198
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:07,820
She'll be right back, okay?

199
00:11:13,680 --> 00:11:15,199
Hey, Ice Queen

200
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,739
What's all this about?

201
00:11:16,740 --> 00:11:18,939
Why don't you pick on someone your own temperature?

202
00:11:18,940 --> 00:11:21,419
My name is not Ice Queen, kitty cat

203
00:11:21,420 --> 00:11:22,640
It's Stormy Weather

204
00:11:22,700 --> 00:11:23,699
Listen to me

205
00:11:23,700 --> 00:11:26,919
I'm feeling more generous than usual today

206
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:37,599
So calm down and let's end this here, okay?

207
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:40,579
I always thought cats landed on their feet

208
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:44,199
Thank you, Ladybug, but I've got this

209
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:46,579
No need for boyish charm, Cat Noir

210
00:11:46,580 --> 00:11:47,719
But you're welcome

211
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:52,380
We're expecting lightning right now, immediately!

212
00:11:52,420 --> 00:11:54,660
Huh!

213
00:12:09,940 --> 00:12:12,140
You won one cat fight

214
00:12:14,180 --> 00:12:15,720
Cat Noir!

215
00:12:26,620 --> 00:12:30,680
Gotcha!

216
00:12:45,440 --> 00:12:50,079
A little Cat Noir will take her wind away

217
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:51,459
Ah, kitty cat

218
00:12:51,460 --> 00:12:53,719
You should think before you move

219
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:54,539
Do you have a plan?

220
00:12:54,540 --> 00:12:57,200
Just follow me

221
00:13:05,620 --> 00:13:08,939
Ah, walk away, you two!

222
00:13:08,940 --> 00:13:10,220
Ah, ah!

223
00:13:15,500 --> 00:13:16,440
Ah, ah!

224
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,700
Ah!

225
00:13:43,800 --> 00:13:45,579
Get out of the ice, hit once

226
00:13:45,580 --> 00:13:48,039
hit twice, and freeze

227
00:13:48,040 --> 00:13:52,579
Hey, that's not fair, you always win, Unicorn!

228
00:13:52,580 --> 00:13:54,279
What was that?

229
00:13:54,280 --> 00:13:55,899
Uh, we...

230
00:13:55,900 --> 00:13:58,940
The Great Goblin King ate too much and his shirt ripped

231
00:14:05,940 --> 00:14:08,539
Do you want to hear a story?

232
00:14:11,500 --> 00:14:15,419
You showed them who the real winner is, my weather girl

233
00:14:15,420 --> 00:14:21,700
But now it's time to do your part of the deal, and here's my plan

234
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:27,139
Maybe she has unresolved anger issues

235
00:14:27,140 --> 00:14:29,139
Or maybe she failed her stress test

236
00:14:29,140 --> 00:14:31,199
Hello, viewers

237
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:35,759
Here's the weather forecast for the first day of summer

238
00:14:35,760 --> 00:14:39,579
Looks like Mother Nature changed her plans

239
00:14:39,580 --> 00:14:41,199
Vacation colors? It's all over now

240
00:14:41,200 --> 00:14:42,039
Already?

241
00:14:42,040 --> 00:14:45,139
But I look great in a swimsuit

242
00:14:45,140 --> 00:14:47,139
Cat suit is enough, thanks

243
00:14:47,140 --> 00:14:49,599
At least we know where to find her

244
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:52,319
Get ready for the worst weather in history

245
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:54,520
You'll freeze to death before long

246
00:14:54,580 --> 00:14:55,980
This girl reminds me of someone

247
00:14:56,020 --> 00:15:00,039
It must be in that akuma umbrella

248
00:15:00,040 --> 00:15:05,020
Winter Wonderland is happening in Stormy Weather's world, on the last slide

249
00:15:09,020 --> 00:15:14,160
No way

250
00:15:22,160 --> 00:15:24,059
and it's going according to my plan

251
00:15:24,060 --> 00:15:26,659
Soon the Miraculous will be mine

252
00:15:26,660 --> 00:15:29,120
Bring them to me

253
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:33,399
Stormy Weather is getting away

254
00:15:33,400 --> 00:15:35,159
Did I hear a damsel in distress?

255
00:15:35,160 --> 00:15:37,679
Some of us don't have night vision

256
00:15:37,680 --> 00:15:39,719
No need to be scared, trust me

257
00:15:39,720 --> 00:15:43,799
Then the one-eyed monster took the princess's hand and

258
00:15:43,800 --> 00:15:47,159
"Look into my eye," he said

259
00:15:47,160 --> 00:15:49,539
Then the princess poked her finger into his eye

260
00:15:49,540 --> 00:15:52,219
As soon as she took a bite of the cursed potato,

261
00:15:52,220 --> 00:15:55,980
the poor princess fell into a deep sleep

262
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:06,920
That's enough!

263
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:09,379
I think from now on, I'll...

264
00:16:09,380 --> 00:16:13,900
Take this, so we can follow you

265
00:16:16,980 --> 00:16:18,019
Empty heads!

266
00:16:18,020 --> 00:16:21,480
You finally fell into my trap

267
00:16:28,880 --> 00:16:33,399
It's time, bring me the Miraculous

268
00:16:33,400 --> 00:16:34,899
No way out

269
00:16:34,900 --> 00:16:36,619
Party's over, fools

270
00:16:36,620 --> 00:16:37,200
It's only just...

271
00:16:39,660 --> 00:16:42,519
It's only just beginning, Stormy

272
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:45,600
Lucky Charm!

273
00:16:49,660 --> 00:16:50,919
A few arms?

274
00:16:50,920 --> 00:16:52,799
What am I supposed to do with this?

275
00:16:52,800 --> 00:16:56,479
Great, we're about to be destroyed, but at least we'll stay dry

276
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:59,500
Just hold on to your whiskers

277
00:17:10,280 --> 00:17:12,339
What's the plan for catching the akuma?

278
00:17:12,340 --> 00:17:15,140
My arms are getting tired

279
00:17:24,100 --> 00:17:27,379
Huh, did you see that sign over there? Take a look

280
00:17:27,380 --> 00:17:29,099
Okay

281
00:17:29,100 --> 00:17:30,020
Disaster

282
00:17:35,080 --> 00:17:39,320
Hey, Cold Spell, is that all you've got to drive someone crazy?

283
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:30,240
Get out of here, you evil bug!

284
00:18:32,720 --> 00:18:34,740
No more evil for you, little akuma

285
00:18:38,860 --> 00:18:42,340
Time to de-evilize!

286
00:18:44,420 --> 00:18:46,279
Got it

287
00:18:46,280 --> 00:18:48,739
Goodbye, little butterfly

288
00:18:48,740 --> 00:18:52,780
Miraculous Ladybug!

289
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:09,519
And after defeating the three-headed dragon in taekwondo,

290
00:19:09,520 --> 00:19:11,719
Yes, the princess kissed the prince and

291
00:19:11,720 --> 00:19:14,099
did they live happily ever after?

292
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:19,340
Yes, until they had a dozen kids who drove them crazy just like you

293
00:19:23,320 --> 00:19:24,879
What am I even doing here?

294
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:26,839
Just you wait

295
00:19:26,840 --> 00:19:29,879
One day, the Miraculous will be mine

296
00:19:29,880 --> 00:19:33,499
I don't know how many enemies I have to send to win, but

297
00:19:33,500 --> 00:19:36,860
victory will be mine

298
00:19:41,680 --> 00:19:45,099
Hey, photographer! Adrien is waiting for you

299
00:19:45,100 --> 00:19:47,039
Aren't we too late?

300
00:19:47,040 --> 00:19:51,039
Come on, Marinette, you saved Manon and the whole world

301
00:19:51,040 --> 00:19:52,140
Have some fun

302
00:19:59,740 --> 00:20:01,199
What? Yellow?

303
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:03,459
Ladybug is your best friend

304
00:20:03,460 --> 00:20:08,660
So now you always know what to do with the other one, you know

305
00:20:11,280 --> 00:20:12,540
Can I be a lollipop?

306
00:20:12,620 --> 00:20:14,259
Please, please, please!

307
00:20:14,260 --> 00:20:15,059
No, Manon

308
00:20:15,060 --> 00:20:16,679
I have important work to do

309
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:20,859
Alya, you'll watch her, right?

310
00:20:20,860 --> 00:20:22,979
I'm ready for the photo shoot

311
00:20:22,980 --> 00:20:24,839
Wait, who's that?

312
00:20:24,840 --> 00:20:25,700
An angel?

313
00:20:30,840 --> 00:20:32,419
Awesome

314
00:20:32,420 --> 00:20:33,539
Perfect

315
00:20:33,540 --> 00:20:34,879
Fabulous

316
00:20:34,880 --> 00:20:36,119
So beautiful

317
00:20:36,120 --> 00:20:38,700
Perfect photos, yes